       2hACAAAAMzQIAAAAMgr3AFcJAQAAADIACAAAADIK9wBsBQIAAAAxNRUAAAD7AkD+AAAAAAAA
       kAEAAAAABAIAEFRpbWVzIE5ldyBSb21hbgAAfgQAAAAtAQEABAAAAPABAAAIAAAAMgrAAfsR
       AgAAAEpzCAAAADIKwAGIDgIAAAAxMAgAAAAyCsAB2wwBAAAAOAAIAAAAMgrAAXkMAQAAACwA
       CAAAADIKwAGnCwEAAAA1AAkAAAAyCsABgwYDAAAAZVZzAAgAAAAyCsABGgMCAAAAMTAIAAAA
       MgrAAWYBAQAAADYACAAAADIKwAH2AAEAAAAsAAgAAAAyCsABKwABAAAAMwAQAAAA+wIg/wAA
       AAAAAJABAAAAAgQCABBTeW1ib2wAAgQAAAAtAQAABAAAAPABAQAIAAAAMgr3AGAQAQAAAC0A
       CAAAADIK9wDyBAEAAAAtABAAAAD7AkD+AAAAAAAAkAEAAAACBAIAEFN5bWJvbAACBAAAAC0B
       AQAEAAAA8AEAAAgAAAAyCsAB+w0BAAAA1wAIAAAAMgrAAV0KAQAAALoACAAAADIKwAGNAgEA
       AADXAAoAAAAmBg8ACgD/////AQAAAAAAEAAAAPsCFAAJAAAAAAC8AgAAAAABAgIiU3lzdGVt
       AAAEAAAALQEAAAQAAADwAQEAAwAAAAAA
      </office:binary-data>
     </draw:image>
    </draw:frame>; si può osservare che cambiando l’ampolla con un’altra che contiene un metallo diverso, la pendenza della retta non varia quindi la pendenza della retta non dipende dal tipo di metallo; la pendenza ottenuta con misure più precise è di <draw:frame draw:style-name="fr7" draw:name="Object15" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="0.8681in" svg:height="0.211in" draw:z-index="8"><draw:object>
      <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block">
       <semantics>
        <mrow>
         <mstyle mathsize="12pt">
          <mrow>
           <mrow>
            <mn>6,6</mn>
            <mo stretchy="false">⋅</mo>
            <msup>
             <mtext>10</mtext>
             <mstyle mathsize="8pt">
              <mrow>
               <mo stretchy="false">−</mo>
               <mtext>34</mtext>
              </mrow>
             </mstyle>
            </msup>
           </mrow>
           <msup>
            <mtext>Js</mtext>
            <mstyle mathsize="8pt">
             <mn>2</mn>
            </mstyle>
           </msup>
          </mrow>
         </mstyle>
         <mrow/>
        </mrow>
        <annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{6,6 cdot &quot;10&quot; rSup { size 8{ - &quot;34&quot;} } &quot;Js&quot; rSup { size 8{2} } } {}</annotation>
       </semantics>
      </math>
     </draw:object><draw:image>
      <office:binary-data>AQAJAAADGgEAAAIAFQAAAAAABQAAAAkCAAAAAAQAAAACAQEABQAAAAEC////AAQAAAAuARgA
       BQAAADECAQAAAAUAAAALAgAAAAAFAAAADAJgAuAIEgAAACYGDwAaAP////8AABAAAADA////
       tP///6AIAAAUAgAACwAAACYGDwAMAE1hdGhUeXBlAABQABUAAAD7AiD/AAAAAAAAkAEAAAAA
